1
00:00:02,969 --> 00:00:04,070
Three minutes.

2
00:00:04,471 --> 00:00:05,571
That's plenty.

3
00:00:05,572 --> 00:00:08,375
You sleep, I'll kiss you.

4
00:00:41,941 --> 00:00:43,610
What's with the pose?

5
00:00:45,645 --> 00:00:46,965
Why are your legs so long anyway?

6
00:00:48,448 --> 00:00:49,582
Wait, are we filming?

7
00:00:50,550 --> 00:00:52,886
Where's the camera? I didn't see it.

8
00:01:02,562 --> 00:01:03,730
Why are you so close?

9
00:01:04,397 --> 00:01:06,066
You're late, stop looking around.

10
00:01:24,184 --> 00:01:25,251
Thanks for the help.

11
00:01:27,020 --> 00:01:28,020
Thank you.

12
00:01:29,722 --> 00:01:30,256
Wait a second.

13
00:01:30,657 --> 00:01:31,657
What?

14
00:01:32,258 --> 00:01:33,258
Get out of the car.

15
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:34,560
No way.

16
00:01:35,762 --> 00:01:36,863
I don't drive.

17
00:01:39,899 --> 00:01:41,301
You don't?

18
00:01:42,135 --> 00:01:44,136
Is it that you won't drive,

19
00:01:44,137 --> 00:01:45,437
can't drive,

20
00:01:45,438 --> 00:01:46,606
or just don't want to?

21
00:01:47,774 --> 00:01:49,075
Stick to your persona.

22
00:01:51,211 --> 00:01:53,313
Don't forget they're recording.

23
00:02:00,520 --> 00:02:01,553
Sorry.

24
00:02:01,554 --> 00:02:02,994
I had a bit of a bathroom emergency.
